{"tid":1686582,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[光復國殤紀念日]11月11日送份大禮俾中共","createTime":"2019-11-01T08:40:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-02T11:27:25.000Z","uid":18728,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"6d2ba404200ec2814ccd97d03f7fc2dea1561038","tid":1686582,"uid":18728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T08:40:19.000Z","msg":"自從淘寶堀起, 每年11月11日Remembrance Day都俾佢地騎劫咗做所謂嘅光棍節<br />\n羞恥嘅係, 香港每年都係佢地境外營業額最高嘅幾個地區, 舊年仲要拎埋第一<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n今年, 大家一定要光復11月11日呢個日子, 由自己開始, 再呼籲身邊朋友唔好參加所謂嘅雙十一優惠, 最好成個十一月都唔好淘寶, 做到嘅, 從此罷買, 我都戒咗兩三年無淘過寶<br />\n<br />\n短期目標: 跌出雙十一營業額最高嘅境外地區頭5名, 11月12日一定會上新聞<br />\n呢個Post係受到早兩日另一位絲嘅idea啟發, 希望大家幫手推推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/53oBSHH.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F53oBSHH.png&h=a41601a5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d80cbcff42b52e8226d044632fd2bafef426cb97","tid":1686582,"uid":18728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T08:40:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/u9jNeWx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fu9jNeWx.jpg&h=a38d5119&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4134b3a9d031d09d93fe13707608c9d5277e5143","tid":1686582,"uid":18728,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T08:42:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bSuA8gW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbSuA8gW.jpg&h=3ba74056&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b8ec721053e66db0ad3eb2f478fcb4a544a45910","tid":1686582,"uid":18728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T08:48:25.000Z","msg":"據報, 產品方面，出口最多是連衣裙、褲、絨毛外套、衛衣、毛針織衫。<br />\n(Source: <a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20181111/58900747\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/li